        B2B buying committees are using AI assistants to build shortlists, define evaluation criteria, and compare vendors — before a single sales conversation takes place.
        <strong class="text-white">GEO for B2B</strong> is the strategy of ensuring your company is cited at every stage of that AI-mediated research journey, from category discovery through to final vendor evaluation.
